# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# MusicGrid lyrics format — LRC with optional translation
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# NAMING:  lyrics file must match the album's image filename.
#          e.g.  image: "mu_1.webp"  →  lyrics: "mu_1.lrc"
#
# FORMAT:  [MM:SS.xx]Original text | Translation text
#
#   • Timestamp    [MM:SS.xx] — minutes, seconds, hundredths.
#                  Thousandths are also accepted: [01:23.456]
#   • Separator    " | " (space-pipe-space) between original and
#                  translation.  Omit it entirely for lines with
#                  no translation.
#   • Translation  Optional per-line and per-song.  The toggle
#                  tab only appears when at least one line has a
#                  translation.
#   • Blank lines and lines not matching [MM:SS] are ignored,
#     so you can use them freely as comments or spacers.
#
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

[00:00.00]♪ | ♪
[00:05.20]First line of the song | Primera línea de la canción
[00:09.80]Second line here | Segunda línea aquí
[00:14.50]This line has no translation
[00:19.10]Back to bilingual | De vuelta al bilingüe
[00:24.00]Instrumental section
[01:02.35]Verse two begins | Comienza el segundo verso
[01:07.90]Carry on | Continúa
